resources.string: XML Umguquleli Free ayikwazanga bamisa internet udibaniso. Qiniseka uxhulumeneyo kwi umsebenzi womnatha kwaye uzame kwakhona.
Olu lwimi ziya zingaphezu yakho 3000 uphawu yonke imihla umda.
Nceda ntaba kuyabhaleka wangaphandle yokugcina eendaba ukuze sebenzisa olu setyenziso.
Funda wangaphandle imvume kuyimfuneko ukufunda isicelo iifayili.
Bhala wangaphandle imvume eyimfuneko ukubhala isicelo iifayili.
Funda Wangaphandle Yokugcina imvume ukuvumela oku app ukufunda kubalulekile app data. Nceda ukuvumela oku imvume kwi-App Izicwangciso.
Bhala Wangaphandle Yokugcina imvume ukuvumela oku app ukugcina ebalulekileyo app data. Nceda ukuvumela oku imvume kwi-App Izicwangciso.
Kuxhomekeke isixa-mali iinguqulelo, le nkqubo ayikwazi kubatshisa enkulu isixa-mali mobile data.
Ngoko ke, kubalulekile advised ukuba ufuna ufumane i-unlimited okanye unmetered lomsebenzi womnatha, phambi ekuqaleni yakho lwimi.
